”Alexa, play Movie Quote Quiz”
”Alexa, open Movie Quote Quiz”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie quote quiz
des:
Upon starting, Alexa will give you a quote, followed by a list of possible movies. Respond with your best guess of either one, two, three, or four. The goal is to get as many questions right as possible, with the highest possible score being five out of five.

UPDATE:

A ton of new questions have been added to make the game even better!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
